Due Date is a 2010 American comedy film directed by Todd Phillips , co-written by Alan R. Cohen , Alan Freedland , and Adam Sztykiel , and starring Robert Downey , Jr. and Zach Galifianakis .
The film was released on November 5 , 2010 .
The film was shot in Las Cruces , New Mexico , Atlanta , Georgia , and Tuscaloosa , Alabama .